        "stories": 2,
        "text": "Great opportunity in Cleveland! This 3-bedroom, 1-bath Cape Cod offers over 1,500 square feet of total living space including a full basement. Built in 1890 with classic character, the home features vinyl siding, a gable roof with asphalt shingles, forced-air heat, and public water and sewer. The layout includes one bedroom on the main floor with additional bedrooms upstairs, plus an unfinished basement offering storage or future potential. Laundry is located in the basement. Appliances including range and refrigerator convey with the sale, along with all items currently in the home. Situated on a platted city lot, this property is ideal for investors or owner-occupants looking for an affordable single-family home."
